('b0317c3f-67b4-5c67-ac10-55b8d2caa5ae', 'e300d4ee-1367-475f-9c2e-2713c0b6f5fd', 'It takes ___ thirty minutes to walk there.', '走路去那裡大約需要三十分鐘。', 'about', 'since', 'during', 'through', '這裡的 about 是副詞，表示「大約」。', '數字前面看到 about，就是「大約」的意思。'),
('ad4de40c-9ee4-5994-bacd-67ad2a4fc4ce', '0d503313-f24a-4195-8140-6fd95a400606', 'Where is my phone? ___ is on the desk.', '我的手機在哪裡？___在桌子上。', 'it', 'he', 'she', 'they', '代名詞：用來指代單數的物品。', '手機是物品，所以用 it。'),
('9a506703-b346-5c97-af43-556c4f7d723a', '056bbf79-2f62-44e1-88e9-19e796ece41a', 'The lawyer read the ___ to the family members in the room.', '律師向房間裡的家人宣讀了遺囑。', 'will', 'diary', 'map', 'note', '名詞，表示遺囑。', 'will → 遺囑 (名詞用法)');
